current.editing_modal_text: While we don't create the entire design ourselves, we can do minor editing to make your custom image look its best on what ever product you are purchasing. The editing we offer includes sizing, color correction, collage work, and the addition of text or card zones. When purchasing a product with editing, we send a preview JPG of the finished image to you before printing to ensure you are happy with the results. This method can add a few extra days to the already 2-4 business days required for production.

settings.title: HIGH QUALITY
settings.body: Every piece of gear that we produce is crafted with the highest level of quality and care. Featuring some of the strongest, smoothest, and sturdiest materials on the market, our products are specifically made to not only enhance your gameplay experience but last you a lifetime.

settings.title: VIBRANT COLORS
settings.body: Muted, fading colors have no place on any of the designs or artworks printed on our products. Instead, our printing process brings our goods to life with the most vibrant and lasting colors one could hope for. These colors are bright, clear and bursting with energy!

settings.title: MADE WITH LOVE
settings.body: Inked Gaming is a company thats made up of 18 tight knit employees who all look out for each other and just love working together. We love what we do, and we see to it that all products are closely inspected for quality. We wouldnt ship anything that we wouldnt use ourselves!

settings.title: DEDICATED TO HELPING YOU GAME IN YOUR STYLE
settings.body: At Inked Gaming, were all about enhancing your game and your style, and weve got a full arsenal of premium, high-quality gaming gear to back it up! Featuring playmats, mousepads, dice bags, binders, dice, sleeves, mat bags, and much more, our website is a one-stop-shop for players of all kinds and calibers, especially those who wish to add a more personal touch with custom gear. Featuring an array of in-store art and customizable design options, Team Inked helps you take your game and play style to the next level!

settings.description: We launched our new site!

We launched our rebrand and introduced our new logo/mascot Kai! Even in the midst of the COVID-19 pandemic, we continued to churn out awesome and essential gear (including face masks) and even managed to get our new Kraken Cards storefront venture off the ground.
We grew our team by adding lots of awesome people, and started the process of another new rebrand!
We started to take a more serious look at bigger picture concepts, like licensing and white labeling. The official Scythe playmat was one of our first officially licensed products.
We added essential gear for transporting/protecting goods to our site and introduced our Gaming Crates and Showcase Binders.
We began to focus on strengthening our presence in the mousepad industry organically, which has paid dividends down the line.

We re-branded and changed our name from Inked Playmats to Inked Gaming in order better represent our expanded line of gaming gear. We also added more goods, like playmat bags and tapestries to our site.
We added dice bags and card sleeves to our arsenal, and bought a new heat press. We also received a big Reddit hug, and had 1 months worth of sales in 1 day!
Our expansion of premium products and gear continued when we added items like mousepads and two-player playmats.
We expanded our growing arsenal of products with fresh, new gear, such as Wargaming Mats and Panoramic desk pads.
Thomas, Jeff, and family launch Inked Playmats. A company started by gamers for gamers. Woo-hoo!
